import styled from 'styled-components';
import { useState } from 'react';

export default function Login() {
  const [email, setEmail] = useState('');
  const [password, setPassword] = useState('');

  return (
    <LoginWrapper>
      <PageTitle>
        Bem vindo! Realize seu Login ou Cadastre novo Posto de Vacinação
      </PageTitle>

      <FormContainer onSubmit={checkCredentials}>
        <label for="email">E-mail: </label>
        <input
          type="email"
          id="email"
          value={email}
          onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}
          required
        />

        <label for="password">Senha: </label>
        <input
          type="password"
          value={password}
          onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}
          required
        />

        <LoginTypesContainer>
          <label for="login-secretaria"> Secretaria de Saúde </label>
          <input
            type="radio"
            name="login-type"
            id="login-secretaria"
            value="secretaria-de-saude"
          ></input>

          <label for="login-posto-vacinacao"> Posto de Vacinação </label>
          <input
            type="radio"
            name="login-type"
            id="login-posto-vacinacao"
            value="secretaria-de-saude"
          ></input>
        </LoginTypesContainer>
      </FormContainer>
    </LoginWrapper>
  );
}
